## Aucctus Chart Styling

### Standard Axis Configuration

```typescript
const aucctusAxisStyle = {
  stroke: 'currentColor',
  opacity: 0.5,
  tick: { fontSize: 11 },
  axisLine: { stroke: 'currentColor', opacity: 0.2 },
  tickLine: { stroke: 'currentColor', opacity: 0.2 },
};

<XAxis dataKey='month' {...aucctusAxisStyle} padding={{ left: 10, right: 10 }} />
<YAxis {...aucctusAxisStyle} width={50} padding={{ top: 10, bottom: 10 }} />
```

### Color Palette

```typescript
const CHART_COLORS = {
  primary: '#7c3aed',      // Purple - main data
  secondary: '#9f7aea',    // Light purple - secondary
  success: '#16a34a',      // Green - positive
  error: '#dc2626',        // Red - negative
  warning: '#f59e0b',      // Amber - caution
  info: '#3b82f6',         // Blue - informational
};
```

### Line Styling

```typescript
// Primary solid line
<Line
  type='monotone'
  dataKey='value'
  stroke='#7c3aed'
  strokeWidth={2.5}
  dot={false}
  animationDuration={1500}
  activeDot={{ r: 6, strokeWidth: 1, stroke: '#fff' }}
/>

// Dashed line (projected data)
<Line
  type='monotone'
  dataKey='projected'
  stroke='#9f7aea'
  strokeWidth={1.5}
  strokeDasharray='4 2'
  dot={false}
  strokeOpacity={0.7}
/>
```

