## Chart Type Selection

### LineChart - Trends Over Time
**Best for**: Time series, financial projections, performance metrics

```typescript
<LineChart data={data} margin={{ top: 10, right: 20, left: 10, bottom: 10 }}>
  <XAxis dataKey='month' {...aucctusAxisStyle} />
  <YAxis {...aucctusAxisStyle} />
  <Tooltip content={<CustomTooltip />} />
  <Line dataKey='value' stroke='#7c3aed' strokeWidth={2.5} dot={false} />
</LineChart>
```

### PieChart - Distributions
**Best for**: Proportions, category breakdowns, test result distributions

```typescript
<PieChart>
  <Pie
    data={data}
    cx='50%'
    cy='50%'
    innerRadius={40}
    outerRadius={75}
    paddingAngle={2}
    dataKey='value'
  >
    {data.map((entry, index) => (
      <Cell key={index} fill={entry.color} />
    ))}
  </Pie>
  <Tooltip content={<CustomTooltip />} />
</PieChart>
```

### BarChart - Comparisons
**Best for**: Comparing values across categories, rankings

```typescript
<BarChart data={data} margin={{ top: 10, right: 20, left: 10, bottom: 10 }}>
  <CartesianGrid strokeDasharray='3 3' stroke='currentColor' opacity={0.1} />
  <XAxis dataKey='category' {...aucctusAxisStyle} />
  <YAxis {...aucctusAxisStyle} />
  <Tooltip content={<CustomTooltip />} />
  <Bar dataKey='value' fill='#7c3aed' radius={[4, 4, 0, 0]} />
</BarChart>
```

